Domain Checker is a free and open-source WordPress plugin that allows anyone to easily check the availability of domain names directly from their website.

With just a simple shortcode, you can embed a domain search tool into your WordPress site. Visitors can instantly check if a domain is available, making it perfect for:

Web hosting companies – Let customers check domains before purchase

Domain resellers – Offer instant domain availability checks

Developers & agencies – Add domain lookup features to client websites

Personal blogs or projects – Just for fun or learning purposes

No coding knowledge is required — simply install the plugin, place the shortcode, and your domain checker is ready to go.

Made with ❤️ by Sunil Kumar
